%% ML Metadata (MLMD) - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant DSPApi as DSP API Server
    participant DSPAgent as DSP Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant MySQL as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    Note over DSPApi, PG: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSPApi->>MLMD: PutExecution (artifacts, events)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS / mTLS
    MLMD->>MySQL: INSERT/UPDATE metadata<br/>MySQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Auth: username/password
    MySQL-->>MLMD: Acknowledgment
    MLMD-->>DSPApi: PutExecutionResponse

    DSPAgent->>MLMD: PutArtifacts / PutContexts<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS / mTLS
    MLMD->>MySQL: INSERT/UPDATE metadata<br/>MySQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS
    MySQL-->>MLMD: Acknowledgment
    MLMD-->>DSPAgent: Response

    Note over DSPApi, PG: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    DSPApi->>MLMD: GetLineageGraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS / mTLS
    MLMD->>MySQL: SELECT lineage data<br/>MySQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Auth: username/password
    MySQL-->>MLMD: Lineage rows
    MLMD-->>DSPApi: GetLineageGraphResponse<br/>gRPC/HTTP2

    Note over DSPApi, PG: Alternative: PostgreSQL Backend

    DSPApi->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>PG: SELECT artifacts<br/>PostgreSQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS (sslmode)<br/>Auth: username/password
    PG-->>MLMD: Artifact rows
    MLMD-->>DSPApi: GetArtifactsByContextResponse
